data.description: Discover your dream home at 2520 Walnut Grove Ave. Modesto! This charming corner-lot residence offers 1,128 sq. ft. of comfortable living space with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Step into the cozy living room adorned with a stone fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. The bedrooms come with ceiling fans, ensuring a pleasant ambiance throughout the year. The well-maintained house features laminate, carpet, and tile flooring, combining both style and practicality. The kitchen is a chef's delight with a pantry closet and elegant tile counters. Built-in 1985, this home is the perfect blend of comfort and style, making it an ideal place to call your own in Modesto.
